{
  "texts": [
    "To operationalize the objectives of the research, they were converted into research questions to identify the mentioned publication metrics.",
    "(RQ1) provides valuable insights into the growth and impact of this interdisciplinary domain.",
    "This information can guide researchers, policymakers, and educators in identifying areas of prominence and potential gaps in the literature.",
    "(RQ2) allows us to recognize key contributors to the field and potentially foster collaborations.",
    "Additionally, (RQ3) helps in analyzing key research themes and prominent keywords to comprehend the evolving discourse and focus of research in this area."
  ]
}